{"type":null,"faqId":18267,"title":"麦芒C199字体如何设置？","answer":"<p>1、进入主题，分类中的字体显示风格，下载自己喜欢的字体，然后应用字体，重启手机后生效。<br>\n2、如果主题中没有在线主题或者分类页，请手动恢复出厂设置（设置-&gt;备份-&gt;恢复出厂设置），请注意备份。<br>\n3、字体效果目前只能针对汉字生效，对英文和数字不生效。<br>\n<br>\n</p>","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":1,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1145","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1421207044000,"seriesProductName":"C199-CL00","visitedTimes":125,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"麦芒,C199,字体,设置","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}